{"title":"用 orgmode 在 hexo 上写博客","date":"2020-03-05T08:52:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年3月5日","L":"2020/03/05","MM-DD":"03-05"},"link":"2020/03/05/hexo","tags":["hexo","org-mode"],"categories":["hexo","org-mode"],"updated":"2020-06-06T09:00:00.000Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><div id=\"content\">\n\n<div id=\"outline-container-org0a8f870\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org0a8f870\">hexo 安装和初始化</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-org0a8f870\">\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init kopinions</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org074783e\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org074783e\">org-mode 配置</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-org074783e\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org17ac725\" class=\"outline-4\">\n<h4 id=\"org17ac725\">安装 org-mode 的 render</h4>\n<div class=\"outline-text-4\" id=\"text-org17ac725\">\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install https://github.com/sjkyspa/hexo-renderer-org --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org9c32e21\" class=\"outline-4\">\n<h4 id=\"org9c32e21\">配置 org-mode 的配置</h4>\n<div class=\"outline-text-4\" id=\"text-org9c32e21\">\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">org:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">emacs:</span> <span class=\"string\">/Applications/Emacs.app/Contents/MacOS/Emacs</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">emacsclient:</span> <span class=\"string\">/Applications/Emacs.app/Contents/MacOS/bin/emacsclient</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">theme:</span> <span class=\"string\">tango-dark</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">highlight:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">enable:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">org:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">htmlize:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">common:</span> <span class=\"string\">|</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">#+OPTIONS: html-postamble:nil</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org0533117\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org0533117\">hexo 启动</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-org0533117\">\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo serve</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org02daa6e\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org02daa6e\">hexo-render-org 支持的行为</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-org02daa6e\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org286b6b4\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"org286b6b4\">plantuml</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-org286b6b4\">\n<p>\nplantuml 是一个支持快速绘制的开源项目。PlantUML 定义了一套领域专用语言实现 UML 关系图的描述。并且基于 Graphviz 图形渲染库进行 UML<br>\n图的生成。在 hexo-render-org 中，自动会下载并且安装 plantuml.jar 并使用 emacs 进行 PlantUML 描述的渲染。<br>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n比如我们有如下的代码片段<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#+BEGIN_SRC plantuml :exports results :file ./xxx.png</span><br><span class=\"line\"> Bob -&gt; Alice: hello alice</span><br><span class=\"line\">#+END_SRC</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n<div id=\"org519bbd0\" class=\"figure\">\n<p><img src=\"/2020/03/05/hexo/plantuml.png\"><br>\n</p>\n</div>\n\n\n<p>\n就可以生成如下图所示的图片文件。具体的 plantuml 的使用方式可以参考 <a href=\"https://plantuml.com/zh/sequence-diagram\">PlantUML 中文</a>.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/kopinions/hexo-renderer-orgmode.git\">hexo renderer orgmode</a> 直接成支持如上 ditaa 的写法，并且会自动生成相应的图片。<br>\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"outline-container-orgbcfbc1b\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"orgbcfbc1b\">ditaa</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-orgbcfbc1b\">\n<p>\nDitaa 是一个支持通文本描述生成通用图标的开源项目。示例如下：<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#+BEGIN_SRC ditaa :exports results :file ./hexo/ditaa.png </span><br><span class=\"line\">  +--------+   +-------+    +-------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">  |        | --+ ditaa +--&gt; |       |</span><br><span class=\"line\">  |  Text  |   +-------+    |diagram|</span><br><span class=\"line\">  |Document|   |!magic!|    |       |</span><br><span class=\"line\">  |     {d}|   |       |    |       |</span><br><span class=\"line\">  +---+----+   +-------+    +-------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">  :                         ^</span><br><span class=\"line\">  |       Lots of work      |</span><br><span class=\"line\">  +-------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">#+END_SRC</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n</div>\n\n<p>\n通过上面的描述，我们可以生成如下图所示的图片。<a href=\"https://github.com/kopinions/hexo-renderer-orgmode.git\">hexo renderer orgmode</a> 直接成支持如上 ditaa 的写法，并且会自动生成相应的图片。<br>\n</p>\n\n<div id=\"org0efed5b\" class=\"figure\">\n<p><img src=\"/2020/03/05/hexo/ditaa.png\"><br>\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"outline-container-org492ccca\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"org492ccca\">dot</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-org492ccca\">\n<p>\nDOT 是一种用于描述文本图形的语言。DOT 提供了一种简单的方式来描述图形，并且这种描述可以被人和计算机所理解。<br>\nDOT 语言通常是具有 .gv 和 .dot 的文件扩展名。 emacs 通过 Graphviz 来支持 DOT 的渲染。<br>\nGraphviz 是 AT&amp;T 实验室启动的开源工具包，可以用于绘制 DOT 语言描述的图形。<br>\n</p>\n\n<p>\ndot 示例如下：<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#+BEGIN_SRC dot :exports results :file ./hexo/dot.png</span><br><span class=\"line\">  graph demo {</span><br><span class=\"line\">      \"Browser\" -- {\"Chrome\", \"Fiefox\", \"Safari\", \"...\"}</span><br><span class=\"line\">  }</span><br><span class=\"line\">#+END_SRC;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n</div>\n\n<p>\n上面的代码生成的图形如下所示。<a href=\"https://github.com/kopinions/hexo-renderer-orgmode.git\">hexo renderer orgmode</a> 直接成支持如上 dot 的写法，并且会自动生成相应的图片。<br>\n</p>\n\n<div id=\"orgdd0b95b\" class=\"figure\">\n<p><img src=\"/2020/03/05/hexo/dot.png\"><br>\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</body></html>","prev":{"title":"OpenGL TransformFeedback 案例和实现考量","link":"2020/04/10/xfb"},"next":{"title":"Mesa3D 详解","link":"2020/02/15/mesa-egl"},"plink":"https://kopinions.com/2020/03/05/hexo/","toc":[{"id":"org0a8f870","title":"hexo 安装和初始化","index":"1"},{"id":"org074783e","title":"org-mode 配置","index":"2"},{"id":"org0533117","title":"hexo 启动","index":"3"},{"id":"org02daa6e","title":"hexo-render-org 支持的行为","index":"4","children":[{"id":"org286b6b4","title":"plantuml","index":"4.1"},{"id":"orgbcfbc1b","title":"ditaa","index":"4.2"},{"id":"org492ccca","title":"dot","index":"4.3"}]}],"reading_time":"524 字约 3 分钟"}